Class JLinkedSlider

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.SwingConstants 

    public class JLinkedSlider
extends javax.swing.JSlider
    This class extends the Swing JSlider class by linking a slider to a "left" and a "right" JTextBox. The right textbox displays the value of the slider and the left JTextBox displays the value (maximum - slider value). The JTextBoxes do not need to be visible.
    Author:
    Originally authored by Dan Rucinski (LimnoTech)
